Author: Alexbt
Title: [BOUNTY] OFFICIAL TRADEPLAYZ BOUNTY CAMPAIGN!
Body: TradePlayz — The Monopoly of the Digital Age in the palm of your hand  When most people see the letters, “ICO”, they think of mass amounts of money, a digital age and cryptocurrency solution to attracting investors, they think of a fast track funding and overnight success that would make Howard Hughes blush. What the letters, “ICO”, should really conjure are thoughts of a team of various talents reaching out to others across the globe endlessly and shamelessly. It’s about the team showcasing their hard work and working around the clock in an endless labor of love to realize their vision of going 100% public. 5 weeks ago, we launched the TradePlayz ICO and began this process. 3 weeks ago we launched the TradePlayz app in the Apple App store and the Google Play store in a bold statement to everyone across the world that we were the top 5% of ICOs out there with an actual product who deserve their attention, support and money.  In the last 5 weeks we’ve seen our Telegram channel go from just under 100 members to 13,000+ and climbing and at an incredible rate. We’ve seen 3,000+ combined downloads of the TradePlayz app, forming a truly global, fantasy cryptotrading community at lightning speed. There’s even been points where there has been so much traffic that it’s been daunting to keep up with all of it. As exhausting as it has been, it has been as humbling as it has been gratifying, in every way. Hearing the feedback and compliments from our user base, and knowing that we’ve not only made a splash, but created an incredible ripple effect points to an ever growing understanding that we’ve created something the public has been waiting for. When you’re building something, you envision the effect it will have on the individual using it, but you don’t really understand every implication that will play out. The physics of it can never be completely predicted, and that mystery is as beautiful and fascinating as it is, by nature, evolutionary and exciting. It’s a palpable experience of innovation moving forward one step at a time after you have poured every gram of who you are into it.  Even now as I’m thinking about this, thinking about each person I’ve communicated with, each investor that has shared their time with me, each team member and advisor that has sunk their teeth into brainstorming through every aspect of what TradePlayz is, I’m still excited and truthfully, a bit breathless, waiting for more. ICO, does stand for “Initial Coin Offering”, wee all know it, but there is a Jekyll and Hyde definition that I’ve coined, “Interminable Continuous Operation”. Sometimes the TradePlayz ICO seems interminable, but April 15 will be here eventually, and with it the money we need to take TradePlayz ahead, into the future. I have very little doubts about that. The process is without a doubt an operation that is continuous, because as a team we’ve created something living, breathing and tangible for everyone with a smart phone after 2.5+ years of hard, hard work that needs constant attention to detail.  From the beginning we’ve understood we had the odds stacked against us — 90% of ICOs fail. 90% of startups die. 90% of investors and capital groups will pass on giving you funding. OK, great! At TradePlayz we always focused on being in the top 5%. We never focused on just being another company and developing just another product in the first place. What would have been the point? We always focused on creating something that hasn’t been accomplished before and have accomplished it! The TradePlayz app isn’t a completely new business platform, it’s true, but it is the first time someone’s accomplished it. Fantasy, real time, cryptotrading that is 100% legal and gives the gift of opportunity to every individual across the globe who has ever wanted to be a trader and learn how to trade. TradePlayz is the Monopoly of the digital age in the palm of everyone’s hand. Arrogantly and confidently, I think, know and believe we’re in the top 5% of ICOs. Why? Because we actually have a product that has the ability to change every person’s life; that isn’t just an idea, concept or a prototype. The best news is that it’s available now! So is the opportunity to buy into it with our ICO to fuel our growth as a company our product that is as lucrative as it is innovative!  The TradePlayz ICO, and its success depends on you! We’ve built something worthy of your money. We want you to buy our ZED tokens. But we want to give something back to you with products that can change your life and everyone’s; and give you back some true rewards in the form of knowledge and money along with it. We’re not just another company with an ICO, we’re an organization with an ICO that can realistically backup why your money is being securely, and purposefully well spent. So, go download the TradePlayz app in the Google Play or Apple App store for your smart phone and see the just the beginning of where your money is going. Go buy your own TradePlayz ZED tokens, and buy into an ICO that deserves your interest and money. “Raise the stakes” by being a part of the Monopoly of the digital age that actually pays you for using your brain. Welcome to TradePlayz and the cryptotrading revolution!  https://medium.com/@TradePlayz/tradeplayz-the-monopoly-of-the-digital-age-in-the-palm-of-your-hand-b481f57fd6ee

Title: [BOUNTY] OFFICIAL TRADEPLAYZ BOUNTY CAMPAIGN!
Body: TradePlayz Official Bounty Campaign Thread The Bounty Campaign will run from January 26th until the end of the TradePlayz Token Sale, April 15th!  THANK YOU EVERYONE! THE BOUNTY CAMPAIGN IS NOW OVER! PLEASE SEND IN YOUR FINAL CLAIM FORMS!! WE WILL HAVE A SPREADSHEET IN THE NEXT WEEK WHICH WILL SHOW HOW MANY ZED WERE EARNED BY EACH PARTICIPANT!  TRADEPLAYZ LINKS [ Website | Whitepaper | Bounty Campaign |  | Facebook | Twitter | Telegram ]      For the Bitcointalk Bounty Campaign, TradePlayz has reserved 1 Million ZED Tokens to be distributed to participants. ZED are ERC20 Tokens which will be distributed among the participants in the bounty campaign based on shares earned in each bounty component, given the allocations for each as seen below.  Bounty Components 1. Telegram/Newsletter Campaign – 5% 2. Bug/Beta Testing Campaign - 20% 3. Translation Campaign – 15% 4. Social Media Campaign (Facebook/Twitter) – 35% 5. Article/Media Campaign – 10% 6. Signature Campaign – 15%   Join the TradePlayz Contest!   IMPORTANT: Once a participant registers with an ETH Address, do not change address throughout the campaign! Only provide ETH address to which you know the private keys or seed phrases. (No exchanges, Shapeshift, or other 3rd party services). Do not send us your private keys! Send us your public ERC20 Address  We look forward to having the support of the Bitcointalk Community and rewarding you all for your work with Tradeplayz (Zed), an ERC20 token designed for the Tradeplayz Gaming Platform. Be sure to check out http://tradeplayz.com to learn more!  We are DONE! PLEASE SUBMIT YOUR FINAL CLAIMS!!!   1. Tradeplayz Telegram Campaign – 5%  Rewards: • Telegram Channel Registration: 1 Share  Guidelines: To earn 1 Share, all you need to do is join our official Telegram channel and fill out the form below. You must remain in the Telegram channel until conclusion of the token offering! Each participant can earn a maximum of 1 Share in this component of the campaign.  How To Apply: Join our Telegram Group Telegram/Newsletter Registration Form  Check Telegram Spreadsheet: Here   2. Tradeplayz Bug/Beta Testing Campaign – 25%  Rewards: • You will be contacted via e-mail once you register. Follow guidelines in order to earn shares.  Guidelines: •All you need to do is register with the Registration Form by sending us your e-mail address. We will contact you and you will be eligible to beta test and earn shares for using our app!  How to Apply: Beta/Bug Testing Registration Form  Beta/Bug Testing Spreadsheet   3. Tradeplayz Translation Campaign – 15%  Official TradePlayz Announcement Thread Link Official TradePlayz Whitepaper Link  Rewards: • Whitepaper Translation: 150 Shares • Whitepaper Updates: 15 Shares Each Update • ANN Thread Translation: 100 Shares • ANN Thread Updates: 2 Shares Each Post • YouTube Video Translation: 20 Shares  Guidelines: • Absolutely no google translator is permitted to be used. Participants using google translator will not be accepted and if a google translation is submitted, that translator will be blacklisted! • Participants may only translate in one language, but can translate both the whitepaper and the announcement thread. • Please do not submit a request to translate unless you are fluent in the translated language and in English. • Announcement Thread translators are expected to moderate the thread and regularly update the thread with news, info, posts, etc from the original meVu Ann Thread or social medias. Each post will earn an additional 2 shares! • If Announcement Thread translators do not make a reasonable attempt to regularly update the thread, a 75% reduction in share will be applied! (75 Shares!). Make minimum 2 updates per week and this reduction will not apply! • Do not begin translating until we have approved your reservation! • Managers/Owners reserve the right to make minor, reasonable changes to the rules.  YouTube Video Translation: In order to earn shares for the YouTube Video Translation, all you must do is translate this text in order to earn 20 shares. At every line, simply mark the time in the video that the line you are translating begins!  Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gX7VoPHaqUM&app=desktop  "Have you considered Binary options? Forex? A stock market burdened by credit? Online casinos?  Forget it!  Earn with your mind. Experience real excitement by playing a fair, honest and exciting game against REAL players.  Analyze statistics, follow news and updates - and make the right conclusions for yourself! Predict the exchange rates! Become better than your opponents and be rewarded!   __  100% Transparency  All transactions are made via Blockchain Technology based on Ethereum.  100% Free until March 1st, 2018  We are giving away up to 1 million ZED through free tournaments, referral programs and for feedback to spread the word about TradePlayz!  ________  Step 1. Download the application (links below); Step 2. Register as a user on TradePlayz Step 3. Participate in exciting tournaments and earn ZED tokens."  How to Apply: To reserve a language, please post your interest along with some of your references following the following format:  • Your Language: • Reference to previous works (at least 3): • Translating Whitepaper, ANN thread or both:  Once accepted, you will be contacted by PM by the Tradeplayz Account and we will post a list of accepted translators here. TradePlayz Social Media Campaign – 35%  Official Tradeplayz Twitter Official Tradeplayz Facebook  Rewards: • 2 Shares / 1 Tweet about TradePlayz • 1 Shares / 1 Retweet of TradePlayz account tweet • 2 Shares / 1 Facebook Post about TradePlayz • 1 Shares / 1 Facebook Share of TradePlayz account post  IN ORDER TO SUBMIT CLAIM FORMS, KINDLY FILL IN YOUR WEEKLY REPORT FORMS HERE WEEKLY. You can submit as soon as you've reached 5, 5, 5, 5 Posts, Tweet, Shares & Retweets. Weekly Twitter Report Form (April 13th to April 15th) Weekly Facebook Report Form (April 13th to April 15th)  Check Twitter Spreadsheet: Here Check Facebook Spreadsheet: Here  Guidelines:  Twitter: • You must first follow @Tradeplayz. • One twitter account per bitcoin talk member is allowed. • Your twitter account must have at least 300 authentic followers. • All tweets will be reviewed by bounty campaign managers. • Twitter Audit must be better than 80% (No Bot Behavior) • MAXIMUM 5 Retweets WEEKLY • MAXIMUM 5 Tweets WEEKLY • MAXIMUM 15 SHARES WEEKLY • A Tweet must include at least one hashtag: #TradePlayz #ZedToken  Facebook: • Follow and like the official TradePlayz Facebook page • One facebook account per bitcoin talk member is allowed. • Your facebook account must have at least 500 friends. • All posts AND profiles will be reviewed by bounty campaign managers. • MAXIMUM 5 POSTS WEEKLY • MAXIMUM 5 FACEBOOK SHARES WEEKLY • Maximum 15 Shares Earned WEEKLY • Posts and Profile must be public.  How to Apply: Twitter Registration Form Facebook Registration Form   5. TradePlayz Articles/Media Campaign – 10%  Rewards: Articles/blog posts will earn 10, 20 or 30 Shares depending on the views, effort level and quality of the post, at the discretion of the TradePlayz team.  Guidelines: • All articles or blog posts must be publicly viewable. • Listing on an ICO tracking / ICO schedule website will earn 30 Shares. • The platform through which you publish must be relevant and there must be an audience. • Pieces should be at least 400 words and include the links to our website (http://tradeplayz.com) and whitepaper (http://tradeplayz.com/tpz_whitepaper.pdf) • Videos must be at least 1:00 long.
